<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.5.7">
<l>muntu nūlum muppu rinūlum muṉṉīnta</l>
<l>anta ṇāḷaṉ piḷḷai yaiyaññāṉ ṟaḷittāṉūr</l>
<l>pontil vāḻum piḷḷaik kākip puḷḷōṭi</l>
<l>nantu vārum paimpu ṉalvāvi naṟaiyūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of him who gave [back] that day the young one of the brahmin</l>
<l>Who had previously given [him] the ancient threads</l>
<l rend="indent">and thrice-twined [sacred] thread,</l>
<l>Is Naṟaiyūr with stepwells of fresh water where a bird runs [in]</l>
<l rend="indent">and scoops up snails,</l>
<l>For the sake of the young ones which live in the hollow [of a tree].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
